11:42.869 --> 11:44.787
playing off the concept

11:44.829 --> 11:46.831
that we all have

11:44.829 --> 11:46.831
specific notions

11:46.873 --> 11:49.209
of gender-appropriate roles.

11:49.250 --> 11:50.835
At least they're

11:49.250 --> 11:50.835
no good at it.

11:50.877 --> 11:52.379
So there we were--

11:52.420 --> 11:54.755
the ocean,

11:52.420 --> 11:54.755
my stepfather and me.

11:54.797 --> 11:56.757
As the storm raged overhead,

11:56.799 --> 11:59.594
he made one final lunge

11:56.799 --> 11:59.594
for the rudder.

11:59.636 --> 12:02.930
I ripped it from his hands

11:59.636 --> 12:02.930
and stared him down.

12:02.972 --> 12:06.184
He knew that I was prepared

12:02.972 --> 12:06.184
to kill him.

12:06.226 --> 12:07.935
I left port

12:07.977 --> 12:10.355
that day a 16-year-old boy.

12:10.397 --> 12:12.731
I returned a man.

12:14.401 --> 12:16.486
That was an amazing

12:14.401 --> 12:16.486
story, sir.

12:16.528 --> 12:18.697
I mean, I was

12:16.528 --> 12:18.697
skeptical at first,

12:18.737 --> 12:20.990
but we do have

12:18.737 --> 12:20.990
something in common.

12:21.032 --> 12:24.785
I mean, look at the way

12:21.032 --> 12:24.785
both our mothers abandoned us.

12:24.827 --> 12:26.787
What are you talking about?

12:26.829 --> 12:28.415
You know, how I was

12:26.829 --> 12:28.415
shipped off here

12:28.456 --> 12:30.584
and you were left with your

12:28.456 --> 12:30.584
wet nurse for all those years.

12:30.625 --> 12:33.794
That story had nothing

12:30.625 --> 12:33.794
to do with my mother.

12:33.836 --> 12:37.798
It had to do with me

12:33.836 --> 12:37.798
finally taking responsibility

12:37.840 --> 12:39.384
for my own actions.

12:39.426 --> 12:41.802
Just sounded like she may

12:39.426 --> 12:41.802
have been a little bit distant.

12:41.844 --> 12:44.097
Well, that is none

12:41.844 --> 12:44.097
of your business.

12:44.138 --> 12:47.267
I swear, you are absolutely

12:44.138 --> 12:47.267
fixated on mothers.

12:47.308 --> 12:48.685
I am not fixated.

12:48.727 --> 12:50.186
Can you name one thing

12:48.727 --> 12:50.186
in your life

12:50.228 --> 12:51.854
that you don't blame

12:50.228 --> 12:51.854
on your mother?

12:51.896 --> 12:53.772
Sure.

12:56.735 --> 12:59.696
(grunts) I'm sorry.

12:56.735 --> 12:59.696
I was just giving an opinion!

12:59.738 --> 13:02.657
Well, it's that pop

12:59.738 --> 13:02.657
psychology nonsense that's...

13:02.699 --> 13:04.825
It is nothing to get

13:02.699 --> 13:04.825
defensive about.

13:04.867 --> 13:06.536
I am not defensive.

13:06.578 --> 13:09.830
Every time anybody

13:06.578 --> 13:09.830
denies a lie,

13:09.872 --> 13:11.499
they're called defensive.

13:11.541 --> 13:13.460
Fine. I take it back.

13:11.541 --> 13:13.460
Your mother was a saint.

13:13.501 --> 13:15.794
I am not saying

13:13.501 --> 13:15.794
that at all.

13:16.963 --> 13:18.839
Does this look anything

13:16.963 --> 13:18.839
like a "Q"?

13:18.881 --> 13:20.216
Reese, just stop this.

13:20.258 --> 13:21.760
You're acting like a moron.

13:21.800 --> 13:23.844
And you're making no

13:21.800 --> 13:23.844
progress with Wendy.

13:23.886 --> 13:26.222
And what the hell do you

13:23.886 --> 13:26.222
need a "Q" for anyway?

13:26.264 --> 13:28.266
You're right. I'm terrible.

13:28.308 --> 13:30.893
I'm just not coordinated

13:28.308 --> 13:30.893
unless I'm hitting somebody.

13:30.935 --> 13:33.020
But I really like her.

13:33.062 --> 13:34.689
I have to get good.

13:34.731 --> 13:36.232
Listen to the words.

13:36.274 --> 13:38.859
Good. Boy. Cheerleader.

13:38.901 --> 13:40.487
Quit while you still

13:38.901 --> 13:40.487
have some dignity.

13:40.528 --> 13:42.071
Oh, and let her think

13:40.528 --> 13:42.071
I'm a quitter?

13:42.113 --> 13:44.865
You can't even remember

13:42.113 --> 13:44.865
a simple six-step routine.

13:44.907 --> 13:47.452
There's six steps?

13:47.494 --> 13:51.038
Yes. It's just right, left,

13:47.494 --> 13:51.038
right, left, reverse, pose.

13:51.080 --> 13:53.333
You remember that

13:51.080 --> 13:53.333
from just watching?

13:53.374 --> 13:56.169
You guys did it,

13:53.374 --> 13:56.169
like, ten times.

13:56.210 --> 13:57.128
So...

13:57.170 --> 13:58.588
you know my routine?

13:58.630 --> 14:00.298
It's not that hard.

14:00.340 --> 14:01.882
But... you know

14:00.340 --> 14:01.882
my routine.

14:01.924 --> 14:03.259
Yes, I do.

14:03.301 --> 14:04.885
Look, I know where

14:03.301 --> 14:04.885
