14:04.927 --> 14:05.886
No, you don't.

14:05.928 --> 14:07.388
You're going to help me.

14:07.430 --> 14:08.889
That  is  where

14:07.430 --> 14:08.889
I was going.

14:08.931 --> 14:10.308
Oh. Good.

14:08.931 --> 14:10.308
Let's get started.

14:10.350 --> 14:12.352
No!

14:10.350 --> 14:12.352
Oh, come on, you have to.

14:12.393 --> 14:13.520
No. Don't you know

14:12.393 --> 14:13.520
