14:14.937 --> 14:17.148
I know what's

14:14.937 --> 14:17.148
more embarrassing.

14:14.937 --> 14:17.148
What?

14:17.190 --> 14:20.901
Getting beaten into a coma

14:17.190 --> 14:20.901
