14:24.781 --> 14:26.907
She was a damn fine woman!

14:26.949 --> 14:28.409
Stick your arms out!

14:28.451 --> 14:29.910
We have to sell this!

14:29.952 --> 14:32.413
Can you move your hand

14:29.952 --> 14:32.413
